title: Marlon Wayans Interview
itunes:title: Marlon Wayans Interview
description:
Today on the show we had friend to the room Marlon Wayans stop by, who spoke on comedic therapy, Chris Rock, T.I., women faking orgasms, his new show on HBO and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Blac Chyna after she said she was just "joking" when she once held unloaded gun around Rob Kardashian. Also, Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee"
